data.description: Welcome to 6133 Kifisia Way, a charming residence in the heart of Fair Oaks, CA. Seller is offering up to $10,000 in credits toward buyer's closing costs or interest rate buydown! This 3-bed 2-bath home offers a traditional floor plan with an abundance of windows that invite bright natural light. The charming exterior offers curb appeal sure to catch the eye. The elegant granite countertops in the kitchen provide a beautiful and functional workspace for all your culinary endeavors. The durable LVP flooring adds to the sophistication. The standout features of this home is the corner lot location and the striking floor-to-ceiling brick accent wall surrounding the fireplace. The primary bedroom offers a private retreat with a convenient backyard patio, where you can enjoy your morning coffee. A hot tub, just one year old, will stay with the property, providing a luxurious way to relax. This home is in an amazing neighborhood known for its friendly community spirit. Located near Folsom Lake, it's easy to enjoy the outdoors. With plenty of shopping centers nearby including Sunrise Mall, all your retail and dining needs will be met. With only a 10-min drive from the freeway, you have easy access to the rest of Sacramento.
